Requirements
1.    welcome message
2.    Ask for user's name
3.    "hello user" message
4.    Ask for permission to start
5.    Generate a random numer
6.    Ask the user to guess the number
7.    If the user is correct congratulate them
8.    if the user is wrong ask again(5 chances only) until correct
9.    Tell to guess higher or lower if the number guessed is higher or lower than the random number
10.   If the user fails 5 times then the game is over
